WEBVTT

00:00.400 --> 00:03.302
♪

00:03.304 --> 00:06.338
<i>Royal guard: It's princess</i>
<i>luna and princess celestia.</i>

00:06.340 --> 00:10.442
Princess twiglight: The everfree
<i>forest is ... Invading.</i>

00:10.444 --> 00:13.145
<i>I think I'm starting to</i>
<i>get a pretty good idea</i>

00:13.147 --> 00:14.646
<i>Of who we're up against.</i>

00:14.648 --> 00:17.082
I'm reformed; don't
you remember?

00:17.084 --> 00:20.052
Why don't you ask
your zebra friend?

00:20.054 --> 00:22.721
You can turn the potion
from purple to white.

00:22.723 --> 00:25.591
You may see why the sky is day

00:25.593 --> 00:27.259
And night.

00:27.261 --> 00:31.597
There can only be one
princess in equestria!

00:31.599 --> 00:35.434
And that princess will be me!

00:35.436 --> 00:38.170
<i>(evil laugh)</i>

00:41.107 --> 00:44.576
<i>♪ my little pony,</i>
<i>my little pony ♪</i>

00:44.578 --> 00:46.512
<i>♪ aaaaahhh!</i>

00:46.514 --> 00:51.183
<i>♪ I used to wonder what</i>
<i>friendship could be ♪</i>

00:51.185 --> 00:53.085
<i>♪ my little pony</i>

00:53.087 --> 00:55.287
<i>♪ until you all shared</i>
<i>its magic with me ♪</i>

00:55.289 --> 00:56.455
<i>♪ big adventure</i>

00:56.457 --> 01:01.727
<i>♪ it's an easy feat</i>

01:01.729 --> 01:06.065
<i>♪ my little ponies</i>

01:06.067 --> 01:09.334
<i>♪ do you know you're all</i>
<i>my very best friends? ♪</i>

01:09.336 --> 01:11.670
♪

01:16.242 --> 01:19.845
<i>(evil laughter)</i>

01:22.749 --> 01:23.849
<i>(zap)</i>

01:23.851 --> 01:25.217
<i>(crash)</i>

01:25.219 --> 01:27.219
<i>(clattering rocks)</i>

01:27.221 --> 01:28.153
<i>(crash)</i>

01:28.155 --> 01:37.496
♪

01:37.498 --> 01:39.264
<i>(zap)</i>

01:39.266 --> 01:40.332
<i>(crash)</i>

01:42.135 --> 01:45.137
Luna! Think of how long you
were banished to the moon.

01:45.139 --> 01:47.306
You'll give us no choice but
to send you back there

01:47.308 --> 01:48.707
If you don't stop.

01:48.709 --> 01:51.343
Luna, I will not fight you.

01:51.345 --> 01:53.345
You must lower the moon.

01:53.347 --> 01:54.580
It is your duty.

01:55.381 --> 01:59.751
"luna", I am nightmare moon!

02:01.421 --> 02:05.691
I have but one royal duty
now: To destroy you!

02:05.693 --> 02:06.692
<i>(zap)</i>

02:06.694 --> 02:07.526
<i>(crash)</i>

02:07.528 --> 02:09.328
♪

02:09.330 --> 02:10.729
And where do you
think you're going?

02:10.731 --> 02:15.400
♪

02:15.402 --> 02:16.368
<i>(zap)</i>

02:16.370 --> 02:19.404
♪

02:19.406 --> 02:21.473
<i>(crashing)</i>

02:21.475 --> 02:26.745
♪

02:26.747 --> 02:27.846
<i>(scream)</i>

02:29.215 --> 02:30.349
Celestia!

02:31.451 --> 02:34.520
<i>(laughing)</i>

02:38.591 --> 02:40.225
No.

02:40.227 --> 02:42.294
Why would luna do this?

02:42.296 --> 02:43.795
Why now?

02:43.797 --> 02:48.333
<i>(sobbing)</i>

02:52.772 --> 02:54.606
You're all right.

02:54.608 --> 02:55.908
You're all right!

02:57.911 --> 02:59.811
Princess celestia?

02:59.813 --> 03:06.718
I am sorry, but you have given
me no choice but to use these.

03:06.720 --> 03:12.558
<i>(grinding)</i>

03:12.560 --> 03:14.893
Are those...The
elements of harmony?

03:14.895 --> 03:16.828
But that's how
they looked in...

03:16.830 --> 03:18.297
The past.

03:19.666 --> 03:21.800
This is the night
you banished her.

03:42.255 --> 03:43.889
(whoosh)

03:43.891 --> 03:53.865
♪

03:53.867 --> 03:59.471
<i>(high-pitched hum)</i>

03:59.473 --> 04:03.609
♪

04:03.611 --> 04:04.710
<i>(explosion)</i>

04:04.712 --> 04:05.877
♪

04:05.879 --> 04:08.847
<i>(high-pitched hum)</i>

04:08.849 --> 04:11.783
Noooooo!

04:11.785 --> 04:13.585
<i>(whoosh)</i>

04:15.655 --> 04:18.991
<i>♪ (peaceful)</i>

04:27.367 --> 04:30.302
Why are you all looking
at me like that?

04:30.304 --> 04:32.838
It's just you were
mumblin' to yourself.

04:32.840 --> 04:35.274
Oh, and don't forget the
uncontrollable sobbing.

04:35.276 --> 04:37.309
We were really
worried about you.

04:37.311 --> 04:40.279
<i>Discord: I, for one,</i>
<i>found it delightful.</i>

04:40.281 --> 04:42.648
Sort of a one-pony theater
piece, if you will.

04:42.650 --> 04:44.983
You should really consider
taking it on the road.

04:44.985 --> 04:46.685
<i>(babyish crying)</i>

04:46.687 --> 04:48.587
Did you find out whose
rump we need to kick?

04:48.589 --> 04:50.322
And where we can find 'em?

04:50.324 --> 04:52.524
I saw something from
a long time ago.

04:52.526 --> 04:54.793
But it didn't explain
what's happening now.

04:54.795 --> 04:58.830
Perhaps farther back still
are the answers you seek.

04:58.832 --> 05:02.668
<i>Another sip of the potion</i>
<i>will give you a peek.</i>

05:02.670 --> 05:04.736
Are you sure about this?

05:08.675 --> 05:09.875
<i>(gulping)</i>

05:10.911 --> 05:15.614
Oh, I do hope she breaks
into a song this time.

05:15.616 --> 05:17.349
<i>(zap)</i>

05:18.851 --> 05:27.359
<i>♪ (eerie)</i>

05:27.361 --> 05:30.662
Ho ho! Ho ho ! This
is so much fun!

05:30.664 --> 05:32.831
How about a game of
pin-the-tail-on-the-pony?

05:34.501 --> 05:38.737
Play time is over
for you, discord.

05:38.739 --> 05:40.505
Oh, I doubt that.

05:40.507 --> 05:42.708
<i>(munching)</i>

05:42.710 --> 05:43.942
Hungry?

05:47.347 --> 05:48.080
Suit yourselves.

05:48.082 --> 05:49.681
<i>(munching)</i>

05:55.888 --> 05:58.657
Oooh. What have
you got there?

05:58.659 --> 06:00.959
The elements of harmony.

06:00.961 --> 06:02.861
With them we shall defeat you.

06:02.863 --> 06:05.597
This must be when they turn
discord into stone.

06:05.599 --> 06:08.734
<i>(mocking laughter)</i>

06:08.736 --> 06:10.836
You should see
yourselves right now.

06:10.838 --> 06:12.738
<i>The expressions on your face.</i>

06:12.740 --> 06:15.841
<i>So intense. So sure</i>
<i>of yourselves.</i>

06:15.843 --> 06:18.677
<i>Ah ha ha!</i>

06:18.679 --> 06:20.112
<i>(zap)</i>

06:20.114 --> 06:21.646
Hilarious!

06:21.648 --> 06:22.714
<i>(guffaws)</i>

06:22.716 --> 06:25.417
<i>(high-pitched buzz)</i>

06:28.087 --> 06:29.554
<i>(gasp)</i>

06:29.556 --> 06:34.559
<i>♪ (peaceful)</i>

06:34.561 --> 06:35.827
<i>(gasp)</i>

06:35.829 --> 06:38.430
The tree of harmony.

06:38.432 --> 06:39.898
The  <u>tree</u> of harmony?

06:39.900 --> 06:47.038
♪

06:47.040 --> 06:48.607
My cutie mark.

06:49.976 --> 06:51.610
<i>(zap)</i>

06:52.712 --> 06:54.579
Are you sure?

06:54.581 --> 06:56.748
We have managed to
discover the only means

06:56.750 --> 06:58.850
By which we can
defeat discord

06:58.852 --> 07:01.720
And free the citizens
of equestria.

07:01.722 --> 07:03.588
<i>Even without these elements,</i>

07:03.590 --> 07:06.992
<i>The tree of harmony will</i>
<i>possess a powerful magic.</i>

07:06.994 --> 07:08.527
<i>(clanging metal)</i>

07:08.529 --> 07:11.563
♪

07:11.565 --> 07:13.198
<i>As long as that</i>
<i>magic remains,</i>

07:13.200 --> 07:17.169
It will continue to control and
contain all that grows here.

07:17.171 --> 07:20.672
♪

07:20.674 --> 07:21.740
<i>(zap)</i>

07:24.177 --> 07:26.011
So, what did
you find out?

07:26.013 --> 07:28.046
I still don't know what's
happened to princess luna

07:28.048 --> 07:30.015
And princess celestia,

07:30.017 --> 07:31.983
But I think I know why
the everfree forest

07:31.985 --> 07:33.018
Is acting this way.

07:33.020 --> 07:35.887
Something's happened
to the tree of harmony.

07:37.690 --> 07:39.558
The tree of what now?

07:39.560 --> 07:41.226
It's where princess celestia
and princess luna

07:41.228 --> 07:42.627
Found the elements.

07:42.629 --> 07:44.229
I think it's in danger.

07:44.231 --> 07:46.731
Well, all right then,
let's go save a...

07:47.633 --> 07:48.867
Tree.

07:48.869 --> 07:51.236
Uh, where is it exactly?

07:51.238 --> 07:53.205
I think it's in there.

07:53.207 --> 07:57.542
<i>♪ (eerie)</i>

07:57.544 --> 08:00.879
I'm going to need
more popcorn.

08:10.957 --> 08:13.525
Seems like only yesterday we
were heading into these woods

08:13.527 --> 08:15.560
To find the elements
of harmony.

08:15.562 --> 08:17.562
Seems like only yesterday
I was foolish enough

08:17.564 --> 08:20.632
To think I should go
after them on my own.

08:20.634 --> 08:22.801
I don't know what we're
going to face in there.

08:22.803 --> 08:26.538
But whatever it is, I know
we need to face it together.

08:26.540 --> 08:27.772
<i>(agreement)</i>

08:27.774 --> 08:34.012
♪

08:34.014 --> 08:35.914
We can use those to cross.

08:35.916 --> 08:38.750
<i>(squeals)</i>

08:40.753 --> 08:42.120
<i>(scream)</i>

08:42.122 --> 08:46.925
<i>Run for your lives!</i>

08:46.927 --> 08:47.692
<i>(skid)</i>

08:47.694 --> 08:51.930
♪

08:51.932 --> 08:53.031
<i>(roar)</i>

08:55.902 --> 08:59.804
<i>(grunts)</i>

08:59.806 --> 09:05.310
♪

09:05.312 --> 09:07.078
<i>Twilight: That was close.</i>

09:08.581 --> 09:11.116
A little too close
if you ask me.

09:11.118 --> 09:12.817
You sure you're
all right?

09:12.819 --> 09:16.087
I just can't seem to get
these new wings to do

09:16.089 --> 09:18.757
What I want them to do
when I want them to do it.

09:18.759 --> 09:20.892
Aw, you'll figure
it out eventually.

09:20.894 --> 09:23.228
"eventually" isn't soon enough.

09:23.230 --> 09:26.298
You have been havin' an awful
lot of trouble with those things

09:26.300 --> 09:30.135
And well, who knows what
else is gonna come after us.

09:30.137 --> 09:32.671
You know, maybe it wouldn't
be such a bad idea

09:32.673 --> 09:36.575
And let us look for the tree
of harmony without her.

09:36.577 --> 09:41.112
For starters, you just about
got eaten by a cragidile.

09:41.114 --> 09:42.280
We all did.

09:42.282 --> 09:48.320
Sure. But... Well, the rest of
us aren't princesses.

09:48.322 --> 09:50.622
What's that got
to do with anything?

09:50.624 --> 09:53.358
Princess celestia and
princess luna are gone.

09:53.360 --> 09:58.263
I just don't think equestria can
risk losin' another princess.

09:58.265 --> 10:00.732
Applejack does
make a valid point.

10:00.734 --> 10:03.001
Even if we manage to
save the tree of harmony,

10:03.003 --> 10:04.869
It won't necessarily
mean princess celestia

10:04.871 --> 10:09.874
Equestria will need somepony
to lead in their absence.

10:09.876 --> 10:13.979
I'm the only one who has seen it
and knows what it looks like.

10:13.981 --> 10:16.348
Huge tree. Cutie
marks on the trunk.

10:16.350 --> 10:19.150
Probably being attacked by
something hideously awful.

10:19.152 --> 10:21.653
Yeah. I'm pretty sure we'll
know it when we see it.

10:23.255 --> 10:25.190
All of you feel this way?

10:25.192 --> 10:27.258
<i>Feel like I shouldn't be here?</i>

10:29.161 --> 10:31.196
It is probably
for the best.

10:39.338 --> 10:41.306
<i>♪ (cheerful humming)</i>

10:41.308 --> 10:44.376
Help! Help!

10:44.378 --> 10:45.644
Discord!

10:47.179 --> 10:48.680
<i>(poof)</i>

10:48.682 --> 10:49.648
<i>(thud)</i>

10:50.349 --> 10:51.883
You're welcome!

10:51.885 --> 10:53.284
Ha.

10:53.286 --> 10:56.121
No luck finding your tree?

10:56.123 --> 10:59.424
We ran into some trouble and my
friends decided it would be best

10:59.426 --> 11:02.360
If I returned to ponyville
while they continue the search.

11:02.362 --> 11:04.329
Equestria will need me if
princess celestia

11:04.331 --> 11:06.431
And princess luna
don't return.

11:06.433 --> 11:09.167
I'm just surprised that
you agreed to their plan.

11:09.169 --> 11:11.102
I never thought you'd
be the kind of pony

11:11.104 --> 11:15.407
Who would think she was
better than everypony else.

11:15.409 --> 11:17.442
I don't think I'm
better than anypony.

11:17.444 --> 11:20.979
Oh! Well, how silly of me to
assume you would think that.

11:20.981 --> 11:24.683
All you did was choose to keep
your precious princess-self

11:24.685 --> 11:27.752
Out of harm's way while your
friends thrust themselves

11:27.754 --> 11:32.424
<i>I'm sure you'll all be</i>
<i>the best of pals again</i>

11:32.426 --> 11:34.726
<i>When they return from</i>
<i>their terrifying,</i>

11:34.728 --> 11:37.395
<i>Yet deeply bonding</i>
<i>experience</i>

11:37.397 --> 11:39.464
<i>That they're having</i>
<i>without you.</i>

11:39.466 --> 11:40.398
<i>(snicker)</i>

11:44.403 --> 11:46.371
I never should have
agreed to come back here.

11:46.373 --> 11:48.406
Come on, twilight,
discord may be reformed

11:48.408 --> 11:50.875
But he's not that reformed.

11:50.877 --> 11:52.777
He's just trying to
get under your skin.

11:52.779 --> 11:54.479
Well, it's working!

11:54.481 --> 11:57.382
♪

11:57.384 --> 11:58.416
<i>(poof)</i>

12:03.289 --> 12:06.825
Anypony else starting to
think this is a lost cause?

12:06.827 --> 12:09.461
We're almost at celestia
and luna's old castle.

12:09.463 --> 12:13.932
When she took that crazy
potion wasn't real.

12:13.934 --> 12:16.167
Maybe there is no
tree of harmony. Maybe--

12:16.169 --> 12:17.802
Maybe it's
right down there.

12:19.171 --> 12:20.505
It can't be.

12:20.507 --> 12:24.109
♪

12:24.111 --> 12:26.277
How are  <u>we</u> supposed
to get to it?

12:26.279 --> 12:29.981
<i>(squeals and grunts)</i>

12:29.983 --> 12:32.817
Take the stairs, silly!

12:34.053 --> 12:35.787
Are we there yet?

12:35.789 --> 12:39.290
I don't know where
we are. We're lost.

12:39.292 --> 12:41.893
I never should've
left my friends.

12:41.895 --> 12:43.495
We can't just give up.

12:43.497 --> 12:46.197
Maybe if I get up there,
I'll be able to spot 'em.

12:50.336 --> 12:52.237
Well, what do you know?

12:53.405 --> 12:54.405
Twilight!

12:55.207 --> 12:58.843
<i>(coughing)</i>

12:58.845 --> 12:59.844
<i>(gasp)</i>

12:59.846 --> 13:01.813
<i>♪ (eerie)</i>

13:01.815 --> 13:04.415
Fluttershy: I think it's dying!

13:04.417 --> 13:06.084
So let's save it already.

13:07.052 --> 13:08.186
<i>(grunts)</i>

13:08.188 --> 13:09.487
<i>(snap)</i>

13:09.489 --> 13:11.022
Nice try.

13:11.824 --> 13:13.424
<i>(battle cry)</i>

13:13.426 --> 13:15.059
Whoa!

13:15.061 --> 13:19.898
But the tree
remains in jeopardy.

13:19.900 --> 13:21.933
And I suppose you've
got a better idea.

13:23.803 --> 13:25.370
That's what I thought.

13:25.372 --> 13:27.806
I know who would
know what to do.

13:27.808 --> 13:29.374
But we sent her home.

13:29.376 --> 13:31.509
♪

13:33.913 --> 13:38.516
♪

13:38.518 --> 13:41.319
It was your idea, applejack!

13:41.321 --> 13:45.190
We all agreed it was the
best thing, rainbow dash!

13:45.192 --> 13:47.225
We were tryin'
to protect her.

13:47.227 --> 13:49.127
<i>(grunts)</i>

13:53.432 --> 13:54.232
Twilight!

13:54.234 --> 13:54.999
Trouble!

13:55.001 --> 13:55.967
Help!

14:01.874 --> 14:03.508
<i>(zap)</i>

14:03.510 --> 14:04.909
<i>(snap)</i>

14:05.277 --> 14:06.444
<i>(thud)</i>

14:09.282 --> 14:12.450
Listen here, you
rabid rhododendrons.

14:12.452 --> 14:15.320
You mess with one of us.
You mess with all of us.

14:15.322 --> 14:16.588
<i>(party noisemaker)</i>

14:16.590 --> 14:18.289
<i>(hiss)</i>

14:18.291 --> 14:19.390
Up here!

14:19.392 --> 14:21.092
<i>(whoosh)</i>

14:22.328 --> 14:24.996
Yoo-hoo! Come
and get me.

14:24.998 --> 14:26.231
Don't forget about me!

14:34.039 --> 14:35.139
<i>♪ ta-da!</i>

14:35.141 --> 14:36.074
<i>(screech)</i>

14:36.076 --> 14:37.175
<i>(pop)</i>

14:42.648 --> 14:45.083
I sure am glad you
came lookin' for us.

14:45.085 --> 14:47.552
Not as glad as I am
that you found me.

14:47.554 --> 14:51.556
The truth of it is, twilight,
we're simply lost without you.

14:51.558 --> 14:55.260
Yeah. Equestria may
need its princess...

14:55.262 --> 14:57.962
But we need our friend.

14:57.964 --> 14:59.998
♪

15:04.270 --> 15:11.142
<i>♪ (eerie)</i>

15:11.144 --> 15:12.110
<i>(gasp)</i>

15:12.112 --> 15:13.978
<i>(zap)</i>

15:15.214 --> 15:17.682
<i>(rustling)</i>

15:17.684 --> 15:22.587
<i>The tree of harmony will</i>
<i>possess a powerful magic.</i>

15:22.589 --> 15:26.024
<i>As long as that magic remains,</i>
<i>it will continue to control</i>

15:26.026 --> 15:28.126
And contain all that grows here.

15:31.630 --> 15:33.631
I know how we can save the tree.

15:33.633 --> 15:36.534
We have to give it the
elements of harmony.

15:38.070 --> 15:40.138
Whoa. Whoa. Whoa.

15:40.140 --> 15:42.373
How are we supposed
to protect equestria?

15:42.375 --> 15:47.078
If we can't use the elements
to turn him back to stone?

15:47.080 --> 15:49.514
Twilight, the
elements of harmony...

15:49.516 --> 15:52.116
They're what keep us
connected no matter what.

15:53.285 --> 15:55.053
You're right about
one thing, applejack.

15:55.055 --> 15:58.022
The elements of harmony
did bring us together.

15:58.024 --> 16:00.491
But it isn't the elements
that will keep us connected.

16:00.493 --> 16:05.129
<i>And it's more important and</i>
<i>more powerful than any magic.</i>

16:05.131 --> 16:09.067
May mean I have to take
on new responsibilities.

16:09.069 --> 16:11.135
And our friendships
may be tested.

16:11.137 --> 16:14.639
<i>But it will never,</i>
<i>ever be broken.</i>

16:14.641 --> 16:16.107
There's no time to lose.

16:16.109 --> 16:17.342
Everypony ready?

16:18.077 --> 16:19.143
All: Ready!

16:20.279 --> 16:25.283
<i>♪ (chimes)</i>

16:25.285 --> 16:31.089
<i>♪</i>

16:31.091 --> 16:32.223
<i>(whoosh)</i>

16:35.494 --> 16:36.627
<i>(horrified gasps)</i>

16:37.329 --> 16:38.529
<i>(grunt)</i>

16:38.531 --> 16:42.567
♪

16:42.569 --> 16:47.205
<i>♪ (heavenly music)</i>

16:47.207 --> 17:00.151
<i>♪</i>

17:00.153 --> 17:14.565
<i>(zaps and rushing)</i>

17:14.567 --> 17:15.633
<i>(thud)</i>

17:15.635 --> 17:17.702
Oh, poo!

17:19.238 --> 17:20.738
<i>(zap)</i>

17:20.740 --> 17:31.149
♪

17:31.151 --> 17:40.825
♪

17:40.827 --> 17:43.227
We know how difficult it
must have been for you

17:43.229 --> 17:44.829
To give up the elements.

17:44.831 --> 17:47.331
It took great courage
to relinquish them.

17:50.135 --> 17:56.407
<i>(rising energy sounds)</i>

17:56.409 --> 18:01.279
<i>(zaps)</i>

18:07.686 --> 18:09.454
<i>(whoosh)</i>

18:09.456 --> 18:12.657
♪

18:12.659 --> 18:14.125
What's inside it?

18:14.127 --> 18:15.660
How am I supposed to open it?

18:15.662 --> 18:18.463
<i>Celesia: Six locks.</i>
<i>Six keys.</i>

18:20.799 --> 18:23.301
I do not know
where they are.

18:23.303 --> 18:25.470
But I do know that
it is a mystery

18:25.472 --> 18:27.605
You will not be
solving alone.

18:35.481 --> 18:37.748
Bravo, ladies! Bravo!

18:37.750 --> 18:39.817
How ever did you save
the day this time?

18:39.819 --> 18:44.155
Blast a beastie with your
magic necklaces, I presume?

18:44.157 --> 18:49.127
You know, the ones you
use to send me back

18:49.129 --> 18:51.896
To my extremely
uncomfortable stone prison.

18:51.898 --> 18:52.730
<i>(sigh)</i>

18:52.732 --> 18:53.631
Gone.

18:53.633 --> 18:54.832
Gone? Ha ha.

18:54.834 --> 18:56.868
Gone?

18:56.870 --> 18:59.637
But our friendship remains.

18:59.639 --> 19:03.841
You'll stop thinking whatever
it is you're thinking

19:03.843 --> 19:05.343
And help us clean up.

19:06.378 --> 19:07.645
Fine.

19:07.647 --> 19:10.181
But I don't do windows.

19:10.183 --> 19:12.150
One thing I don't get.

19:12.152 --> 19:14.252
Why'd all this happen now?

19:14.254 --> 19:16.420
<i>Discord: I have no idea.</i>

19:16.422 --> 19:19.524
Those seeds I planted
should've sprouted up ages ago.

19:19.526 --> 19:21.259
What did you say?

19:21.261 --> 19:23.161
Oh. Why should I
try to explain it,

19:23.163 --> 19:25.496
When you can see
for yourself?

19:28.200 --> 19:29.500
<i>(gulping)</i>

19:30.769 --> 19:31.936
<i>(zap)</i>

19:31.938 --> 19:35.873
Play time is over
for you, discord.

19:36.675 --> 19:38.543
Oh, I doubt that.

19:40.380 --> 19:45.416
Well, obviously things didn't go
<i>according to my original plan.</i>

19:45.418 --> 19:47.885
<i>My plunderseeds should</i>
<i>have stolen the magic</i>

19:47.887 --> 19:52.256
<i>And captured princess</i>
<i>celestia and princes luna</i>

19:52.258 --> 19:54.425
<i>Thousands of moons ago.</i>

19:54.427 --> 19:57.795
<i>Alas, it seems the tree</i>
<i>had enough magic</i>

19:57.797 --> 20:01.832
<i>To keep the seeds from</i>
<i>growing up big and strong.</i>

20:05.204 --> 20:08.839
You realize this is information
we could have used hours ago?

20:08.841 --> 20:12.843
And rob you of a valuable
lesson about being princess?

20:12.845 --> 20:15.713
What kind of friend
do you think I am?

20:15.715 --> 20:16.747
(snap)

20:21.286 --> 20:23.821
<i>♪ (fanfare)</i>

20:23.823 --> 20:36.334
♪

20:36.336 --> 20:40.972
Citizens of equestria, it is
no longer with a heavy heart,

20:40.974 --> 20:44.942
But with great joy, that
I raise the summer sun.

20:44.944 --> 20:47.378
For this celebration
now represents,

20:47.380 --> 20:49.880
Not the defeat of
nightmare moon,

20:49.882 --> 20:54.018
But the return of my
sister, princess luna.

20:54.020 --> 20:58.589
<i>(cheers)</i>

20:58.591 --> 21:12.336
♪

21:12.338 --> 21:13.938
<i>(whoosh)</i>

21:13.940 --> 21:16.274
♪

21:16.276 --> 21:18.409
<i>(gasps of amazement)</i>

21:18.411 --> 21:24.282
♪
